  "intro": "<p> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一入空门，一落红尘<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n 一样的山水清音<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n 忘却往事前尘，追念曾经缘因<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n 又见沧海风云</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一落红尘，一入空门</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一样的明月禅心</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">你踏风履尘，我沉静山林</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">笑看世事纷纭</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">上山，把心安放，踏遍红尘，把爱供奉。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">下山，是灵魂的再一次洗礼，从未忘记心愿，让那美好延续。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2017年5月，桑吉平措成为秦皇岛市三宝山风景区旅游形象代言人，在美丽的三宝山中有一座北魏时期的古老庙宇---摩诃寺。由于传统文化的回归，新的摩<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">诃寺院也正在修建，现任住持释明心法师也正在为这座古老庙宇的复建奉献着力量。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一首歌，一份心意。愿善水长流，善心永驻，桑吉平措再次奉献词曲创作，燃起那份对善念的供养。《上山下山》 这首歌描述的是世间“善的力量”不计身份、不分你我的无私奉献，那是一种人性固有的、源于本心的大爱至善。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">每一种善的信仰，都是一颗爱与和平的种子。它们相生相伴、共同成长，这盛开的每一朵花，结出的丰硕果，都是那汇聚善的力量所浇灌。 </span></p>\n <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br>\n </span>\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">《上山下山》歌词</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">作词/作曲：桑吉平措</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">编曲 ：郭易 吉他 ：王昊 </span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">录音：刘家昌 缩混：王广武（中国台湾）</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">一入空门，一落红尘，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">一段因缘，一次轮回。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">一个回家，一个寻家，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">一路随缘，一生了缘。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">心相传，故往正在眼帘，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">意相连，因果就在面前，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">前生言，今生共度莲潭，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">此时诠，如是我闻续缘。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">一个上山，愿力呈现，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">一个下山，迷雾眷恋。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">三宝山上，慈悲心间，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">三宝山下，皈依心路。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">心相传，故往正在眼帘，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">意相连，因果就在面前，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">前生言，今生共度莲潭，</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">\n <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 12px;\"=\"\">此时诠，如是我闻续缘。</span> </p>",
